
#import "../../../_lib/kodama.typ": *

#show: kodama

#metadata((
  title: [Cartesian space],
))

Write $serif("CartSp")$ for the category whose
- objects are Cartesian space $RR^n$
- morphisms are suitable structure-preserving functions between these spaces.
For definiteness we write
- $serif("CartSp")_"lin"$ for linear functions
- $serif("CartSp")_"top"$ for continuous functions
- $serif("CartSp")_"smooth"$ for smooth functions


